      "para_id": "Q001194.2",
      "line_range": "2",
      "translation": "(i 1') ..., whose name was proclaimed by Enlil , chosen by Nanše in the heart , who makes the foreign lands submit to Ninĝirsu , ..., ( when Ninĝirsu ) placed all lands in his hand , and placed the rebellious lands at his feet , ...."
    }
  ],
